Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.36,0:00:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有茜姐一起去沖繩我感覺踏實多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拿到有薪假期真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.10,0:00:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好久沒和姥爺見面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.69,0:00:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能查明你媽媽的事就更好了 慶太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩添飯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是第四碗了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要多吃點 打倒哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…也要戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填補者只要戰鬥就會不斷消耗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艾克塞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼時候交換的手機號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴她要去沖繩也沒關系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們明天似乎要去沖繩 我派下位元神靈去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比瑢大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我重要的遊樂場弄得一團糟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利士郎 把他們找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 黎真大人找您有事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有黑大人 誰也不能對她下手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:56.33,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲しみが宿った眼に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:56.33,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我悲傷的瞳孔中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:58.69,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映しだす　君のmotion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:58.69,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映出了你閃動的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:02.83,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思いが流れてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:02.83,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思憶潮水般湧來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.73,0:02:06.21,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求められ選択した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.73,0:02:06.21,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我選擇了他們想要的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:08.76,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その答えは　そうfusion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:08.76,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可在這選擇的作用下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:12.76,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛みが導く先にある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:12.76,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現的卻是痛苦的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:18.04,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黒い闇　迫っても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:18.04,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是在黑暗面前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.04,0:02:23.00,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑顔をいつもくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.04,0:02:23.00,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑容始終依舊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:28.19,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光を護るため
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:28.19,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了守衛光明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:35.21,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君と今　ひとつになれる…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:35.21,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我此刻與你融為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:41.04,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追いつけないほどの力　手に入れて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:41.04,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得讓人望塵莫及的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:45.56,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風を切って貫いてゆけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:45.56,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後去穿透烈風吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:50.70,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰を信じてる…？　通じ合えたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:50.70,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能相互信任理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:55.56,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡起こせる　何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:55.56,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能不斷創造奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:03:01.48,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真実いつか　見えるから…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:03:01.48,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能最終發現真相
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起關心我 還是快點幹掉他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無意義的戰鬥還是盡量避免的好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跑掉就最好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別做夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:31.07,i,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 07 「小黑的過去」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶了泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳衣 和內衣不一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是遊泳的時候穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜姐胸部的脂肪太多 遊泳減減也好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:03:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們 是下位元神靈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:03:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難對付
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里央奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就說 怎麼跑得掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窩裏鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 能放過我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑 不用幫他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利士郎大人在等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個遊弋的元神靈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一上來就動手不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 膝蓋都擦破了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點擦傷就能了事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揶雲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您沒事太好了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑小姐是我們族的大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑是大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是揶雲在找的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小暮里央奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揶雲 我也訂契約了 和這位慶太先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒感覺到有容量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是填補者嗎 我是主根源
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主根源是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里央奈從幫她成為主根源的魁音寺財團逃了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魁音寺是擁有K-ON MART 食品工廠甚至酒店的大財團吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是暗地裏卻在制造主根源
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主根源
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為主根源的人都處在財團的管理下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣食無憂 要什麼有什麼 過得倒不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被派去參加一個什麼實驗 然後就逃了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行實驗的似乎是比瑢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比瑢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就遇見揶雲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松手 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看這樣 他挺厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揶雲可是哥哥的大弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能因為我是主根源運氣好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我就拜托他和我訂契約了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主動要求的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要力量保護我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為聽說成了契約者能變強
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魁音寺財團制造主根源做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說有個大人物把主根源都帶到沖繩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沖繩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:08:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大人物就是黎真大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎真是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我牽扯進來了總得說清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得對大小姐無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐是統帥著最高貴的獅子神族的巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎真是我的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 我把一切都告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 要你破費
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揶雲 嘴邊弄臟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去便利店買點創可貼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別靠近K-ON Mart
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有魁音寺的攝像頭監視著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一族居住在異界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是個有結界保護的清凈之地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清凈之地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是元神靈居住的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在那裏守護著共存均衡 安穩地生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是發生在祭祀靈石儀式前某一天的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的清凈之地有靈石守護 容量非常充足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是外面的世界卻沒有這麼多的容量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你沒去外面看過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和哥哥一起什麼地方都沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎真 小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要進行夢蔔儀式了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子神的女巫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 是怎樣的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 並不是不祥之夢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和巫女大人一樣亮麗的頭發
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長得真美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揶雲 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 少主把全族的人都殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 哥哥他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.02,0:11:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著巫女大人到靈石那去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥他 怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又裂開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道真的是哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼要殺媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在要去下界 去創造新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把全族的人和媽媽都殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆我者亡 我要毀掉世界的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和這個清凈之地一起枯竭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去殺掉哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你哥哥連自己的母親也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.97,0:13:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何把清凈之地和族人看得比什麼都重的哥哥會這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會根據答案決定是否殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我要去沖繩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑大人 終於見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比瑢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比瑢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為把人類帶到清凈之地實驗而被流放的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了那個實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才能把元神靈的力量分給人類量產下位元神靈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎真大人也很認可我的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個殺掉巫女大人來到人界的黎真
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你成為我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 不過之前先得行刑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種家夥和黑大人訂契約實在罪不可赦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比瑢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:14:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人的心臟在這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比瑢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑大人你也要保護猴子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太是我重要的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和容量如此稀薄的人訂契約 是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是契約者就同步給我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看你的容量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.01,0:15:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填補者連同步也不敢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比瑢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑大人 讓我來使你覺醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會很溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:16:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑 同步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只能戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 黑大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我見識下你的全部容量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越技 滅牙得救世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的超越技怎麼可能打倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越技沒有用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太他們怎麼還沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別去什麼沖繩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:16:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說句住手就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你抱著求我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見識下我的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比瑢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股可疑的容量原來是你的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揶雲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到自己送上門了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里央奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揶雲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑大人 過不久我就會向你介紹我的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揶雲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被揍了幾下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過揶雲救了我 已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比瑢大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現小暮里央奈和元神靈了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比瑢大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好叫忍來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普尼普尼 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微忍下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也沒了媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得難過就哭出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽死時我哭得可兇了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你也沒必要忍著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒叫你在這哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是填補者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是訂了契約就要和你一起戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到還清救命之恩為止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:07.35,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつしか朝を迎え
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:07.35,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺已至清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:12.45,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凍てつく躰溶けて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:12.45,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僵硬的身體開始恢復溫度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.65,0:21:18.57,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覚めた記憶で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.65,0:21:18.57,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我整理思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:24.30,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早すぎた死を還して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:24.30,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕了再度襲來的睡意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:30.29,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲たちの鳴く聲も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:30.29,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲兒低鳴的聲音消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:36.30,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥たちの舞う羽音にも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:36.30,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥兒展翅的聲音也沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:42.30,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音を亡くした　白き涸れ地に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:42.30,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬籟俱靜　一片慘白的荒蕪大地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:48.40,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あふれる彩を　そそいでいく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:48.40,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地被陽光染上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:52.17,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あざやかに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:52.17,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絢麗的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.78,0:21:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太熱的地方我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:21:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我一個人去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 打算放著契約者不管嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揶雲 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克塞爾 施泰納
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.13,0:22:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是The Noble One的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Noble One
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.67,0:22:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來送我們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.32,0:22:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有東西給他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著 這是戰鬥裝身具Thousand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.31,0:22:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是以契約者為觸媒發動特殊能力的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.77,0:22:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand只能感應契約者純粹的容量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好帶在身邊練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.98,0:22:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要給我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.60,0:22:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠過來讓我仔細看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長得還行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.21,0:22:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 不能看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太骯臟了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.05,0:23:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.94,0:23:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能從危機中拯救元神靈的只有契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:11.78,o,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode 「緋馬一族」
